body: "GH-606. .toon item files use count-prefixed array headers (notes[N]{...}, tags[N], tests[N]); concurrent commutative appends hard-conflict, and hand-resolution with a stale count makes the item unreadable by pm get while validate skips it silently (pm-cxyv). Authoritative-state twin of pm-wc1r (history layer). Fix direction: .toon-aware merge driver or count-header-free serialization; at minimum validate must hard-fail on header/data disagreement."
